veteran guards that have passed the age of retirement but still want to uphold
justice and protect their dear city of Kir Drax'in.  This proud warrior now
stands here befouled by vile Necromantic magicks to become the zombified
puppet standing before you.  The armor is tattered and age-worn, the weapons
are pitted and brittle due to decay.  Perhaps this poor wretched soul can be
put back to his honorable slumber once more.  
