the undead corpse of Lieutenant Orbeshi~
A decomposing corpse belonging to the late Lieutenant Orbeshi of the Kir Drax'in Guard is twitching violently here.
~
   Lieutenant Orbeshi was a tall, commanding presence in life, and his stony
face still hints at his former person.  He wears a formerly bright red coat
with brass buttons and could almost pass for a live person, except the
remainder of his body below his waist lay in ruins.  Whatever forces have
reanimated this man, they force his ruined lower appendages to work despite
their state.  What were once his legs are now a mash of sinew, bone, and
muscle seemingly haphazardly forced together to create an inhuman twitching
movement that is terrifyingly fast.  
~
