the reanimated corpse of Lieutenant Wolfsbane~
A decomposing corpse belonging to the late Lieutenant Wolfsbane of the Kir Drax'in Guard is shuffling about here.
~
   A face half peeled away to reveal the shiny white bone underneath stares in
stark terror.  His eyes stare at an unknown horror as he relives the last
moments of his life repeatedly.  He bellows loudly, "Flank him, men!  The
Behemoth must have a weak spot.  Find it and aim true!" He stands ready to
charge, a broken longsword in his right hand.  His left arm ends at the elbow,
but he doesn't appear to notice as he thrusts it out in front of him as if he
were holding a shield.  
~
